{
  "sentences": [
    {
      "paraIndex": 0,
      "sentIndex": 0,
      "text": "一个春日，曹操请刘备到小亭里坐坐。",
      "audioPath": "audio/p1_s1.wav",
      "durationMs": 0,
      "unavailable": true
    },
    {
      "paraIndex": 0,
      "sentIndex": 1,
      "text": "桌上有青梅，锅里冒着热气，院外竹叶轻轻响。",
      "audioPath": "audio/p1_s2.wav",
      "durationMs": 0,
      "unavailable": true
    },
    {
      "paraIndex": 0,
      "sentIndex": 2,
      "text": "曹操想看看刘备怎样看人，便笑着问：天下谁称得上英雄？",
      "audioPath": "audio/p1_s3.wav",
      "durationMs": 0,
      "unavailable": true
    },
    {
      "paraIndex": 1,
      "sentIndex": 0,
      "text": "刘备听了，先没有急着回答。",
      "audioPath": "audio/p2_s1.wav",
      "durationMs": 0,
      "unavailable": true
    },
    {
      "paraIndex": 1,
      "sentIndex": 1,
      "text": "他想起许多有名的人，也想起路上见过的普通百姓。",
      "audioPath": "audio/p2_s2.wav",
      "durationMs": 0,
      "unavailable": true
    },
    {
      "paraIndex": 1,
      "sentIndex": 2,
      "text": "刘备说，有力量的人很多，可真正的英雄，应当懂得照顾别人，也愿意承担责任。",
      "audioPath": "audio/p2_s3.wav",
      "durationMs": 0,
      "unavailable": true
    },
    {
      "paraIndex": 2,
      "sentIndex": 0,
      "text": "曹操又问，难道英雄只靠名声吗？",
      "audioPath": "audio/p3_s1.wav",
      "durationMs": 0,
      "unavailable": true
    },
    {
      "paraIndex": 2,
      "sentIndex": 1,
      "text": "刘备摇摇头，说名声像风，会来会去；",
      "audioPath": "audio/p3_s2.wav",
      "durationMs": 0,
      "unavailable": true
    },
    {
      "paraIndex": 2,
      "sentIndex": 2,
      "text": "心里的仁义和做事的勇气，才更要紧。",
      "audioPath": "audio/p3_s3.wav",
      "durationMs": 0,
      "unavailable": true
    },
    {
      "paraIndex": 2,
      "sentIndex": 3,
      "text": "他说话不大声，却很清楚，也没有夸耀自己。",
      "audioPath": "audio/p3_s4.wav",
      "durationMs": 0,
      "unavailable": true
    },
    {
      "paraIndex": 3,
      "sentIndex": 0,
      "text": "这时天边响起一声春雷，刘备仍然从容坐着。",
      "audioPath": "audio/p4_s1.wav",
      "durationMs": 0,
      "unavailable": true
    },
    {
      "paraIndex": 3,
      "sentIndex": 1,
      "text": "曹操看着他，心里知道这个人不简单。",
      "audioPath": "audio/p4_s2.wav",
      "durationMs": 0,
      "unavailable": true
    },
    {
      "paraIndex": 3,
      "sentIndex": 2,
      "text": "刘备却只是低头看青梅，谦虚地说，自己还要多学习，多帮助百姓。",
      "audioPath": "audio/p4_s3.wav",
      "durationMs": 0,
      "unavailable": true
    },
    {
      "paraIndex": 4,
      "sentIndex": 0,
      "text": "小亭里的谈话很短，却让人记住：看一个人，不只看他会说什么，也看他遇事是否从容，心里是否装着别人。",
      "audioPath": "audio/p5_s1.wav",
      "durationMs": 0,
      "unavailable": true
    },
    {
      "paraIndex": 4,
      "sentIndex": 1,
      "text": "真正的英雄，常常先把责任放在前面，也会照亮身边的人。",
      "audioPath": "audio/p5_s2.wav",
      "durationMs": 0,
      "unavailable": true
    }
  ]
}
